			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Well I am only a &quot;lowly&quot; 54 wiz,but I am surprised by the posts so far.  None of you know the first thing about using agro to your advantage.  The root/stun idea won't work.  THe sword has 100hps which means that unles you perfectly chain stun, one hit and the sword go POOF.  Same thing with PVP...100hps of dmg at this level amounts to a halfling sneezing!! No I'm convinced my method is the best and simplest.  You SNARE the mob and then you must nuke it once or twice (BTW IC may do massive dmg but it's terribly Mana ineficient ppl...get real).  Anyways the nukes should be enough to get agro completely on you.  Only at this point do you cast the sword.  Keep snaring...keep running..keep nuking if you want.  The idea is that the snared mob chases you, the sword chases the mob, and if you play your agro right, the mob will never attack the sword and it can do an AMAZING amt of dmg over the lifetime of the fight with a relatively minimum of mana.  <BR>
I have many levels until I get this spell, but rest assured, TRU SOLOING WIZZYS know how to use this to their advantage &lt;evil grin&gt;
