				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I think this was posted earlier but most of you don't know how to look at previous pages so I'll restate it again.<BR>
<BR>
This is a great spell.  Take for instance the broken golem in PoF.  Roughly around 150k hp's.<BR>
<BR>
You cast this at the beginning of the fight...you cast your ice comet a few times and now you need to med because your OOM.  The golem still has 3/4 life left and it's not going down anytime soon.<BR>
<BR>
Instead of being useless while medding, you have you trusty flaming sword out their doing dmg at 50pt whaps.<BR>
<BR>
Yes it only has 100hps but it will not get killed because it will never agro the stupid mob.  It's the Wizzy's Kick ASS DOT spell.  For 700 mana you hit and hit and hit and hit.<BR>
<BR>
Multiply this times 10 wizzys that cast it, now you have 10 hitting for 500dmg total per hit.  Over time wizzys have contributed quite a bit!<BR>
<BR>
Get the idea?
